http://daeso.uvt.nl
e.marsi@gmail.com


 
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	DESCRIPTION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The DAESO Framework is a Python library developed in the DAESO (Detecting And
Exploiting Semantic Overlap) research project. It supports working with
collections (corpora/treebanks/graphbanks) of aligned similar
(parallel/comparable) text. It provides the foundation for the Hitaext
and Algraeph corpus annotation tools, and for the language-specific DAESO
Dutch library.


